name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Etsy Tag Extractor by Ali Kaan BAŞHAN

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Etsy Tag Extractor by Ali Kaan BAŞHAN

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: It is a plugin that shows you the tags of that product when you enter the products on the Etsy site and allows you to copy the tags when you press the button. If you have a store on the etsy site and you want to see the tags of the products published by other stores, you can use this plugin.
